Bottle.  
Appearance: Dark with a Tan Head.
Aroma:  Smells like a cup of coffee.
Flavor: Taste of roasted coffee with a hint of chocolate.
Palate:  Great mouth feel and smooth finish.
Bottle.  Think and black with a nice tan head.  Taste of chocolate and coffee.   Smells of roasted coffee.
Bottle.   Nice level of hops but it would be even better if they could have gotten a little better balance.
Pitch black color with a nice tan head.  Aroma of chocolate and coffee.   Nice flavor of chocolate to start and espresso on the finish.   Very nice soft finish and light mouth feel.
